{"tid":240954,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"當生活有詩，我們會不一樣","createTime":"2017-05-12T19:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T14:20:37.000Z","uid":114590,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"080479775602b023cf54b6bb8261dab1b9a50eff","tid":240954,"uid":114590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T19:10:20.000Z","msg":"平時好鍾意寫詩，一有題材就會儲埋佢，之後再發展成一首詩。<br />\n<br />\n而寫詩都係需要有閱讀詩嘅習慣，今日就推薦一個網路畀大家。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cendalirit.blogspot.hk/?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcendalirit.blogspot.hk%2F%3Fm%3D1&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2Bv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=a10a4f4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cendalirit.blogspot.hk/?m=1</a><br />\n<br />\n由一班台灣文學愛好者建立嘅網站，每日挑選一首好詩，加以介紹同賞析，深入淺出咁畀大家接觸好詩。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/cendalirit/?locale2=zh_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fcendalirit%2F%3Flocale2%3Dzh_HK&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2Bv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=5a7e0d06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/cendalirit/?locale2=zh_HK</a><br />\n佢地仲有Facebook fans page 添，大家可以去like。<br />\n<br />\n之後要介紹嘅係香港電台節目--和你說說詩。<br />\n如果上面嘅係熱身操，啲個節目就係健身環節。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rthk.hk/radio/radio2/programme/poem_with_you\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Fradio%2Fradio2%2Fprogramme%2Fpoem_with_you&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2Bv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=780157d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.rthk.hk/radio/radio2/programme/poem_with_you</a><br />\n<br />\n由香港著名詩人--廖偉棠主持，每集會分享唔同詩人，有時一集講一個，有時分兩集。<br />\n<br />\n咁有為你選好嘅，都有擂台之必要。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.taiwanpoetry.com/phpbb3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=71719&amp;sid=6940bf523d7aac5faa8c65d4fad179c7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.taiwanpoetry.com%2Fphpbb3%2Fviewtopic.php%3Ff%3D7%26t%3D71719%26sid%3D6940bf523d7aac5faa8c65d4fad179c7&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2Bv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=b98a51f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.taiwanpoetry.com/phpbb3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=71719&amp;sid=6940bf523d7aac5faa8c65d4fad179c7</a><br />\n吹鼓吹詩論壇就係你去闖嘅地方，有人會睇你嘅詩，批評你嘅詩。同時你可以係啲個地方揾到好多具備質素嘅作品。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家生活中會有詩，咁就可以揾到救命嘅欄杆。<br />\n<br />\n最後送大家一首詩。<br />\n<br />\n生活 陳子謙<br />\n一滴水的自殺方法：<br />\n投湖<br />\n<a href=\"http://readreadpoetry.blogspot.hk/2016/07/blog-post_2.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Freadreadpoetry.blogspot.hk%2F2016%2F07%2Fblog-post_2.html%3Fm%3D1&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2Bv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=0799a4e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://readreadpoetry.blogspot.hk/2016/07/blog-post_2.html?m=1</a><br />\n<br />\n有詩，或者可以令我們抽身於麻木。"},{"pid":"75860dcccb098f1186fe3424efb957baf644157c","tid":240954,"uid":114590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T19:13:01.000Z","msg":"雖然知道題目不吸引，但希望有人會睇。"},{"pid":"2f7d55d1601f4597c4ae8825942e4fd89bbd025b","tid":240954,"uid":114590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T19:13:30.000Z","msg":"如果有人有興趣，我可以繼續寫落去。"},{"pid":"22a4458d24cdd4c67f52fbb1fca43c7f80a16b44","tid":240954,"uid":7915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T19:15:39.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"19e114dbbe414a9fc94a731c06a5aad6fa1f1b86","tid":240954,"uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T19:15:58.000Z","msg":"你覺得咩野係詩？"},{"pid":"86982e16287d2ba5cc3b12cd053f558ddf2c0cc2","tid":240954,"uid":107324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T19:16:08.000Z","msg":"留明等詩"},{"pid":"03d7a9ca00da5e88eda552c7d4f40183cf0bd045","tid":240954,"uid":36701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T19:16:19.000Z","msg":"有試過學寫詩,但係覺得好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb4a7509af7ccf86162aaa5e5d240d37955e78d","tid":240954,"uid":56984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T19:17:24.000Z","msg":"支持，鐘意文學，雖然唔太識新詩，但都想學。<br />\n<br />\n觀眾雖少，一人足矣。"},{"pid":"ee90874e1d26dd51c72f0f2cbae8edb206aa10cd","tid":240954,"uid":114590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T19:17:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你覺得咩野係詩？</blockquote><br />\n上堂老師都問過啲個問題，我唔知，但我一直都視詩係一個岀口，情感岀口。"},{"pid":"77a507c49aa8fb212c3f61b5ddf4fef39c790c03","tid":240954,"uid":114590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T19:20:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有試過學寫詩,但係覺得好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n難啲點在於邊到。"},{"pid":"e7f1f578bb8beabdb9a7235e60feb0e27202ca7f","tid":240954,"uid":114590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T19:22:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持，鐘意文學，雖然唔太識新詩，但都想學。<br />\n<br />\n觀眾雖少，一人足矣。</blockquote><br />\n多謝。希望可以令你踏出第一步先。"},{"pid":"63c518260221afaee9f7988eb222b0707bf8460a","tid":240954,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T19:22:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb8ad1663f9e0500fb89b562d1db039bc9c58bc1","tid":240954,"uid":36701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T19:32:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有試過學寫詩,但係覺得好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n難啲點在於邊到。</blockquote><br />\n好難寫到自己感覺,掌握唔到寫詩要啲咩技巧"},{"pid":"a370ba6d999145f21e82793d94da0ed60f6f7ad8","tid":240954,"uid":114590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T19:38:22.000Z","msg":"有時失意，我哋唔係需要安慰，而喺一個振作嘅理由。於是我們要......<br />\n<br />\n好好---林季鋼<br />\n　<br />\n好好吃<br />\n好好睡<br />\n惡意的夢<br />\n只有在晚上出現<br />\n明天的陽光一定同樣善良<br />\n善良如你<br />\n一個好好的人<br />\n一個人<br />\n也要好好<br />\n　<br />\n好好笑<br />\n得知最悲傷的事<br />\n或者好好大哭一場<br />\n如果生病<br />\n就要好好吃藥<br />\n病毒是唯一一個進入你以後<br />\n再也不會離開你的<br />\n好好跟著<br />\n好好相處<br />\n到目的地之前還有一大段路<br />\n　<br />\n好好擁抱迎面而來的人<br />\n擦肩而過的<br />\n好好道別<br />\n坦然面對自己真的無能為力<br />\n接受別人的心意<br />\n好好收著<br />\n　<br />\n好好愛人<br />\n好好對待整個宇宙<br />\n好好照顧自己<br />\n好好活著<br />\n　<br />\n好好活著才能明白<br />\n活著好好<br />\n　<br />\n<br />\n林季鋼，台灣詩人，網路詩人。<br />\n佢喺咁介紹自己嘅：「我愛你，這便是我身為生物最可悲的向性。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/TheRemainder/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FTheRemainder%2F&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2Bv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=428e36c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/TheRemainder/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://macacasapiens.blogspot.tw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmacacasapiens.blogspot.tw%2F&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2Bv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=692df6ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://macacasapiens.blogspot.tw/</a>"},{"pid":"11025c6a3f4834ec4081c9ce2bb4e393ef28b6c4","tid":240954,"uid":114590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T19:55:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有試過學寫詩,但係覺得好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n難啲點在於邊到。</blockquote><br />\n好難寫到自己感覺,掌握唔到寫詩要啲咩技巧</blockquote><br />\n感覺，就真係要多寫，寫寫下就拿揑到。<br />\n<br />\n而技巧，可以講無技巧，但可以從睇唔同嘅詩，去知道點掌握詩嘅方法。寫詩有人好似捉棋，每一步都計算得好準確，每一首詩都係文字遊戲;同時又可以係場賭博，跟感覺去。所以詩，係揾適合你嘅方法寫就可以。<br />\n<br />\n介紹兩本書畀你。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.books.com.tw/products/0010498256\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.books.com.tw%2Fproducts%2F0010498256&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2Bv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=83e88217\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.books.com.tw/products/0010498256</a><br />\n《遊戲把詩搞大了》喺一本用遊戲教人寫詩嘅書。幾有趣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.books.com.tw/products/0010470229\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.books.com.tw%2Fproducts%2F0010470229&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2Bv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=7710aa00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.books.com.tw/products/0010470229</a><br />\n《蕭蕭教你寫詩、為你解詩》簡單，有系統，將唔同類型嘅詩好系統咁教學，好易明。"},{"pid":"d3c2ae75e2aa3da5bc8c71b0745be9ad0a157835","tid":240954,"uid":85226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T14:08:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a4e5e52b1cc53fa2a30c7c66395494aa178439","tid":240954,"uid":114590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T14:20:37.000Z","msg":"同大家介紹一個詩人，叫鯨向海。<br />\n喺一個精神科醫生，今年40歲。<br />\n佢發表詩作起步在網路上面。<br />\n<a href=\"http://old.ltn.com.tw/2001/new/jan/30/life/article-1.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fold.ltn.com.tw%2F2001%2Fnew%2Fjan%2F30%2Flife%2Farticle-1.htm&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2Bv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=570f9cbb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fold.ltn.com.tw%2F2001%2Fnew%2Fjan%2F30%2Flife%2Farticle-1.htm&h=2e4329c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://old.ltn.com.tw/2001/new/jan/30/life/article-1.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n之後係2002年岀版第一本詩集《通緝犯》。<br />\n入面嘅詩作係集合佢寫詩初期頭五年嘅作品。<br />\n有關於青春嘅詩"}]}